        <div class="section-label">Our Story</div>
        <h2 class="section-heading" id="about-heading">A People of Becoming</h2>
        <p>
          HAYAH is a prophetic expression drawn from the Hebrew word הָיָה,
          meaning "to be, to exist, to become, and to come into manifestation."
          It is a word deeply rooted in Divine activity, revealing God as the
          One who not only is, but who causes things to be.
        </p>
        <p>
          From the very beginning, in Genesis, creation itself responded to the
          voice of God — what He spoke became. This is the essence of Hayah.
          This same revelation is echoed in Exodus 3:14, where God reveals
          Himself as <em>"I AM"</em> — the Self-Existent One, the Eternal
          Source, and the God of manifestation.
        </p>
        <p>
          Hayah International Ministries Inc. is therefore raised as a Divine
          commission to embody and proclaim this reality — to be a vessel
          through which the purposes of God are not only declared but birthed
          into manifestation.
        </p>
        <div class="about-pillars" role="list" aria-label="Our Mandate">
          <div class="pillar fade-up" style="transition-delay:0.18s" role="listitem">
